        "description": {
            "value": "<p>With a sudden shout, a well-timed taunt, or a cutting put-down, you can shake an enemy&rsquo;s resolve. Choose a creature within 30 feet of you who you&rsquo;re aware of. Attempt an Intimidation check against that target&rsquo;s Will DC. If the target does not understand the language you are speaking, you&rsquo;re not speaking a language, or they can&rsquo;t hear you, you take a &ndash;4 circumstance penalty to the check. Regardless of your result, the target is temporarily immune to your attempts to Demoralize it for 10 minutes.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Critical Success The target becomes frightened 2.</p>\n<p>Success The target becomes frightened 1.</p>",
